eventText: Dominik contacts Christa for solving ADA Apple account issue.
Christa was in meetings all day on 13Feb. She is available now to solve the account issue.

Franks sends email to set up a meeting with christa next week.
Sambhaji checks the iTunesConnect account. The issue is solved now. Sambhaji sends a confirmation to Christa with screenshot.
Harshit requests Shrinath to add testers for ADA app.
@19Feb, 6:46PM, ADA testers are invited to test the ADA app. Shrinath informs Dominik.
Dominik sends tow new testers for ADA app. Sambhaji forwarded the information to Harshit and Neville.
Dominik says that Erika and Neumiller has not received the invitations. We are sending the invitations again.
Invitation for testing the app is now sent to Erika, Neumiller. Shrinath informs Dominik.
